{"tid":1941612,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人對捉手帶依個city hunt 上哂癮","createTime":"2020-03-24T13:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T02:17:13.000Z","uid":50769,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9585f21f1c6ae25cd144c1af865f1caaf28bba74","tid":1941612,"uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"出街金晴火眼咁望有無人帶手帶出街 食飯會望一望周圍有無隔離人士<br />\n邊個著長袖衫邊個就係鬼"},{"pid":"4a7ab1c0f0bd5ff426dec4b1a57ec660259ef2d3","tid":1941612,"uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40d269be7f08b489667548ff2e9f944e2c0955b","tid":1941612,"uid":48124,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T02:21:04.000Z","msg":"有無留意到呢幾日有好多傳媒都好似夾埋咁大做「帶着手帶離家出走自私撚」既故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後林鄭配合聲淚俱下，每次記者會都喺度屌鳩呢啲人自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本上就係想將大家將個怒氣spin落捉鬼捉自私撚，慢慢淡化林鄭一開始唔封關嘅事，同時支持政府加大監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乘機推行d監控嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由二月中至三月頭，由支那陸路入境嘅人一直冇需要帶任何手帶，淨係間中喺電話分享location就當隔離左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢啲嘢又冇人講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下次見到有「哇有個手帶人又去XXX食嘢」呢一類post，嘗試下唔好講「 仆你個街又係呢啲自私撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n試吓講「呢啲自私撚固然唔應該出街，但最仆街嘅都係林鄭一開始唔支那封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />害死全香港人」"},{"pid":"f5270781e7edc96c2d4feb1ebe1d0802142b3ef3","tid":1941612,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"冇 唔出街"}]}